title: PENYEMPROTAN RUTIN UNTUK MENCEGAH DAN MEMBASMI KUTU PUTIH #pertanian #durian #ediduren

tasks.task: Performing agricultural treatments to prevent white frost damage on trubis plants.
subtasks: Applying magnesium sulfate to the trubis plants.
Using a pesticide (komisida) on the trubis plants.
Spraying or treating trubis plants with a botanical fungicide (fitoplank).
Regularly checking the trubis plants to monitor for white frost damage.
